OL,3,CKelly Osbourne responds to negative
OL,4,Ccomments during 'hardest time in my
OL,5,Clife'
OL,7,FTV personality Kelly Osbourne has
OL,8,Fspoken out after receiving negative
OL,9,Fcomments on social media while she is
OL,10,F"going through the hardest time in my
OL,11,Flife".
OL,13,FHer father, Black Sabbath frontman
OL,14,FOzzy Osbourne, died aged 76 in July
OL,15,Flast year, having been diagnosed with
OL,16,FParkinson's disease in 2019.
