OL,3,CKelly Osbourne responds to negative
OL,4,Ccomments during 'hardest time in my
OL,5,Clife'
OL,7,FThe singer, known as the Prince of
OL,8,FDarkness, was honoured with a
OL,9,Fposthumous lifetime achievement award
OL,10,Fat the Brit Awards on Saturday, with
OL,11,Fhis widow Sharon and daughter Kelly
OL,12,Fcollecting the accolade on his behalf.
OL,14,FFollowing the awards ceremony, it has
OL,15,Fbeen reported that Kelly received
OL,16,Fnegative comments online such as
OL,17,Fpeople criticising her appearance.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
