OL,3,CKelly Osbourne responds to negative
OL,4,Ccomments during 'hardest time in my
OL,5,Clife'
OL,7,FOsbourne posted on her Instagram story
OL,8,Fon Sunday to "defend herself", and in
OL,9,Fthe message to her 4.4 million
OL,10,Ffollowers, she wrote: "There is a
OL,11,Fspecial kind of cruelty in harming
OL,12,Fsomeone who is clearly going through
OL,13,Fsomething.
OL,15,F"Kicking me while I'm down, doubting
OL,16,Fmy pain, spreading my struggles as
OL,17,Fgossip, and turning your back when I
OL,18,Fneed support and love most.
OL,26,@pD@NOUpD@]O]rD@WOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
