OL,3,CKelly Osbourne responds to negative
OL,4,Ccomments during 'hardest time in my
OL,5,Clife'
OL,7,F"None of it proves strength; it only
OL,8,Freveals a profound absence of
OL,9,Fcompassion and character.
OL,11,F"I'm currently going through the
OL,12,Fhardest time in my life. I should not
OL,13,Feven have to defend myself. But I
OL,14,Fwon't sit here and allow myself to be
OL,15,Fdehumanised in such a way."
OL,17,FOsbourne has previously posted about
OL,18,Fthe criticism she has received on
OL,19,Fsocial media, and last week she shared
OL,20,Fa screenshot of negative comments
OL,21,Fbeneath her Instagram post.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUwD@[O]
