OL,3,CKelly Osbourne responds to negative
OL,4,Ccomments during 'hardest time in my
OL,5,Clife'
OL,7,FAt the Brit Awards, Sharon remembered
OL,8,Fher late husband as "authentic, gifted
OL,9,Fand unpredictable", as his legacy to
OL,10,Fmusic was recognised during the
OL,11,Fceremony.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, Kelly thanked the audience
OL,14,Ffor loving her father "as much as we
OL,15,Fdo" and referencing the football team
OL,16,Fsupported by Ozzy ` Aston Villa ` she
OL,17,Fsaid: "I hope I don't disrespect
OL,18,FManchester by saying this, but up the
OL,19,FVilla and Birmingham forever."
OL,26,@pD@UOUqD@RO]vD@WOUwD@CO]yD@GOU{D@^O]
