OL,3,CKelly Osbourne responds to negative
OL,4,Ccomments during 'hardest time in my
OL,5,Clife'
OL,7,FOne of the founding members and
OL,8,Ffrontman of Black Sabbath will be
OL,9,Fhonoured in recognition and
OL,10,Fcelebration of this impact and
OL,11,Finfluence to rock music worldwide.
OL,13,FThe Osbourne family are no strangers
OL,14,Fto The BRIT Awards.
OL,16,FOzzy hosted the awards in 2008, along
OL,17,Fwith his family Sharon, Kelly and Jack.
OL,19,FBlack Sabbath's eponymous debut album
OL,20,Fin 1970 made the UK top 10 and paved
OL,21,Fthe way for a string of hit records.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
