OL,3,CKelly Osbourne responds to negative
OL,4,Ccomments during 'hardest time in my
OL,5,Clife'
OL,7,FThey went on to become one of the most
OL,8,Finfluential and successful metal bands
OL,9,Fof all time, selling more than 75
OL,10,Fmillion albums worldwide.
OL,12,FThe group were inducted into the Rock
OL,13,FAnd Roll Hall of Fame in 2006, and
OL,14,FOsbourne was added for a second time
OL,15,Fin 2024.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/8
