OL,3,CKelly Osbourne responds to negative
OL,4,Ccomments during 'hardest time in my
OL,5,Clife'
OL,7,FIn July 2025, thousands of fans
OL,8,Fvisited the Black Sabbath Bench on
OL,9,FBroad Street in the musician's home
OL,10,Fcity to lay bouquets, wreaths,
OL,11,Fposters, balloons, candles and cards,
OL,12,Fand line the street for his public
OL,13,Ffuneral procession.
OL,15,FHis death came only a few weeks after
OL,16,Fthe band's Back to the Beginning
OL,17,Fconcert at Villa Park, where the band
OL,18,Fcelebrated its roots and connection to
OL,19,FBirmingham.
